
 * Build the application and prepare it for the deployment.
 Stores all files in specified folder (dist).
 main.js is much lower size than after ng serve command.
 - ng build

 * Serve an application on localhost.
 - ng serve

 * install specific version of angular cli:
 - npm install @angular/cli@1.6.5

 * sometimes it is hard to remove angular cli version, but it can be removed from node_modules safely,